headline: Apple (AAPL) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Apple (AAPL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +10.56% and +5.75%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
